---
title: Seared Salmon & Peppercorn Hollandaise with Potato Mash & Garlic Veggies
description: Sometimes all you need to be happy is a good cut of salmon, a mash and pan-fried veggies. Let’s put a smile on everyone’s face
by drizzling over a peppercorn Hollandaise sauce, dark and rich with flavour. It’s smiles all around!
